      <Placemark>
        <name>Gedong Sisi Ubud</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gxon8uSjC4p9j3Ji2QQpBC0z72dUex2eG4PMVGf7w4fzveMP_JkwqJVdfsXPJ_3ORsg3jENELnFGa63gRzmTOVg3LNhZUOFaKVDWFrdVKaok9rlDsQ8szPf8a908QxPd8eIZbX48hbTQHJbVk4bDmLFaaJensI24RMX9mbk0TfKHBWe6vuQDhjxPf6IzD605r3fdAO1tHiT_3nrdG2C1B5Zuw0rXW9GWPM9wZgTSfVZwKiFeCd-XBQ0IoM?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>在烏布有一間餐廳是我每次造訪峇里島的必訪之地，它的名字叫做Gedong Sisi Udud，就位於烏布皇宮側門大街約100公尺的距離，地理位置相當便利。<br>這家餐廳散發著濃厚的峇里島傳統風情，不僅環境充滿當地特色，餐點品質更是令人讚不絕口。他們的印尼風味料理水準相當出色，但最讓我驚喜的是，就連義大利麵也做得極為精緻美味，完全超乎預期。<br>從大街上就能清楚看到這間開放式餐廳的招牌門面，非常好辨識。如果您有機會到烏布一遊，我強烈推薦您前往品嚐，相信絕對不會讓您失望。（劉燦榮 社長提供）<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gxnysbbw5V-ggsXbHd8eMI1QP1R2Tv4sMHvuMu6jjYsf8BRfGr7GXPXlLeg4D3KIGUXDxYh6fdjGScXAGUzrN5FZLFPBKoz3z3LoUqErrhKRed_B0H2xUUjZzDcv488AmW_k6a-4KDt-SHsx_1IMDmZ9lMQGjlBl-5BkWSQViuQSzBdYzVnke03qBW8vP0xDrv8SdXEla2gFIRv4V5PcxQ1BuuAbQdlqT9SRtQyn7yZGCkCQDSsZaihQMc?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GycSbYq46YGxpFZv1ZXsVAJR-WHvtakd0BpWIV9jVo1cCBs39xayqmEMUiusiCVHfoTKdf2A4OMyFiHK9IpElLXiU4Vv1zmmED2NQ-FwTiOOPusRrc9h15mgjuNAGr6DmVEMPaSgyeSad47wNXxOr7nXpeFDi8aYxgZnMhKu3mwjYrc9a_0-Vkf98XZ888Q7BVxh79a7wohzJvXgW-Ed5PKfwwzqkOI7LfqelUuLsbdfNtogcf13nrYNvo?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GxbyVy7vDk0HDfbieFaOmoayq5hF8Ty1rb9ZY7BAauk44oB0O2At6jjFkvgOboBELLptMmO4r06HFLa36RY9ln_H5LHgrYnOhzu-qogCbDQUkRX1GFMVbC4zRfJfy_LpApYLpMcoXPCfWKsSChdgVeK0t8dt8yAol7oeKK_CZbIMsSyHARp1MXIRiw4rQxSbRQ59Lo3Z6eggn9DtbSbqdpQB6VUM2fmZ7WM8YKIEG76j4in3Mt8NosgIpo?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gxon8uSjC4p9j3Ji2QQpBC0z72dUex2eG4PMVGf7w4fzveMP_JkwqJVdfsXPJ_3ORsg3jENELnFGa63gRzmTOVg3LNhZUOFaKVDWFrdVKaok9rlDsQ8szPf8a908QxPd8eIZbX48hbTQHJbVk4bDmLFaaJensI24RMX9mbk0TfKHBWe6vuQDhjxPf6IzD605r3fdAO1tHiT_3nrdG2C1B5Zuw0rXW9GWPM9wZgTSfVZwKiFeCd-XBQ0IoM?authuser=0&fife=s16383 https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gxnysbbw5V-ggsXbHd8eMI1QP1R2Tv4sMHvuMu6jjYsf8BRfGr7GXPXlLeg4D3KIGUXDxYh6fdjGScXAGUzrN5FZLFPBKoz3z3LoUqErrhKRed_B0H2xUUjZzDcv488AmW_k6a-4KDt-SHsx_1IMDmZ9lMQGjlBl-5BkWSQViuQSzBdYzVnke03qBW8vP0xDrv8SdXEla2gFIRv4V5PcxQ1BuuAbQdlqT9SRtQyn7yZGCkCQDSsZaihQMc?authuser=0&fife=s16383 https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GycSbYq46YGxpFZv1ZXsVAJR-WHvtakd0BpWIV9jVo1cCBs39xayqmEMUiusiCVHfoTKdf2A4OMyFiHK9IpElLXiU4Vv1zmmED2NQ-FwTiOOPusRrc9h15mgjuNAGr6DmVEMPaSgyeSad47wNXxOr7nXpeFDi8aYxgZnMhKu3mwjYrc9a_0-Vkf98XZ888Q7BVxh79a7wohzJvXgW-Ed5PKfwwzqkOI7LfqelUuLsbdfNtogcf13nrYNvo?authuser=0&fife=s16383 https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GxbyVy7vDk0HDfbieFaOmoayq5hF8Ty1rb9ZY7BAauk44oB0O2At6jjFkvgOboBELLptMmO4r06HFLa36RY9ln_H5LHgrYnOhzu-qogCbDQUkRX1GFMVbC4zRfJfy_LpApYLpMcoXPCfWKsSChdgVeK0t8dt8yAol7oeKK_CZbIMsSyHARp1MXIRiw4rQxSbRQ59Lo3Z6eggn9DtbSbqdpQB6VUM2fmZ7WM8YKIEG76j4in3Mt8NosgIpo?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
