    <Folder>
      <name>烏布中心Jl. Monkey Forest</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Wenara Bali Bungalows</name>
        <description><![CDATA[▶Right next to Monkey Forest<br>▶You can see monkeys right in this hotel<br>▶list on a Franch travel magazine as one of the best afforable hotel in Ubud. Many Franch guests came here.<br>▶we stay at Family room 4 nights for NT3,000, not each night, it's the total price. And it includes breakfast. That is NT750 per night<br><br>請參考「烏布攻略」：https://gobaligo.id/go/ubud-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1603-880E4F</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.259275,-8.5171662,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Tukies Coconut Shop（猴子森林路店）</name>
        <description><![CDATA[▶這是一家非常專業的椰子店。你可以找到與椰子有關的所有東西，如椰子油，椰子冰淇淋，椰子片，椰子醬.....等<br><br>請參考「烏布攻略」：https://gobaligo.id/go/ubud-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2610085,-8.5110836,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Watercress Cafe Ubud</name>
        <description><![CDATA[▶從烏布皇宮的路口走過來600公尺<br>▶在水明樣也有一家<br>▶很多評論說是這附近一定要來的餐廳<br>▶很多人說他們的漢堡無敵好吃<br>▶推：雞肉漢堡、雞肉沙爹漢堡、acai bowl、沙拉<br><br>【巴西莓（acai）也音译被称之为“阿萨伊”是生长在亚马逊热带雨林的「生命之树」果实，含有大量抗氧化物和氨基酸。被誉为「全球最棒的超级食物」之一，smoothie bowl的升级版。巴西莓果碗拥有比沙拉更奇妙的瘦身减肥功效，倡导健康轻食欧美网红博主几乎人手一碗】<br><br>請參考「烏布攻略」：https://gobaligo.id/go/ubud-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2610494,-8.5124077,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Starbucks Monkey Forest</name>
        <description>星巴克</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2607023,-8.5131383,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Three Monkeys Ubud</name>
        <description><![CDATA[Large amount of plants=large amount of mosquitos (bring mosqit repellent)<br><br>Large variety of food<br><br>Very calm atmosphere<br><br>the plantations look wonderful<br><br>Summary: The plantations makes the restaurants atmosphere very enjoyable/calm]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
