      <Placemark>
        <name>The Fire Flies Garden</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwNP1gVgTybjVfgqsbfrIA-E0hMR8wfsED-R3N8QxD9jHllJm7gH7W5hmhh87cY4Sj--iyi7RzFI3ECFP5CuLfrPKNb4iSRkCb9k0wynDaM6E4zLkptwfl-hgG59R3P3rtcxanOyp-Nsa23p5iGoMllt37UnwqGucIRXjOPGaDfxXBq-OSsvV7d7fBJ3isFx7k412X_EHQwDutmFnZAPqHBUuNbWXH6DJhcgjqi5RyBzPFpicu_1HxN4nA?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>✨ 峇里島螢火蟲花園奪下生態旅遊大獎！<br>在浪漫夜色下欣賞螢火蟲飛舞 🌌，同時支持保育與有機農業 🌿。<br>👉 下次來烏布，不妨安排一場奇幻的夜間體驗！<br>請參考「烏布攻略」：https://gobaligo.id/go/ubud-guide]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
