      <Placemark>
        <name>Kebun Bistro</name>
        <description>我們這次去雖然最有名的羊排賣完了，但店員推薦的牛排也非常美味！點了五分熟，切開卻沒有血水，肉質非常嫩，連配菜都很好吃。因為顧客很多，建議在正餐時間提前訂位。（連育諄提供）</description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2642122,-8.513603,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Warung Pondok Madu</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwiiIzPnbNr8Y5RA45s0KQMxuiXlxMeAEmE_2wpTIqdGxQ54S94DHSB3L0KYbwbGqPXRY4gny5VijdhtaV9mySb9dFlwmLfPxDDTDiR0QTrZqhrD15EPCMeqynX0iTB2WGbFk5q6WeNr0ufj5fmDXIAWb64FL3kI_vMt5wpdAXGuACJhNpBfzBVvU_6U4jCxf0WXwrty2yNmqEpZCMRL9VEJYY4A_8deKpwI8TlQR9sBPaomilgUh9QTE0?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>回到家已經半個月了，但我仍然無法忘記那一口豬排。這次峇里島之行，我發現了一家不可錯過的豬排店。<br><br>這家餐廳的豬排真的是絕品，每一口都充滿了多汁和濃郁的風味。無論你點什麼，都不會踩雷，真的是讓人一試成主顧。<br><br>更讓人陶醉的是，餐廳的二樓有靠窗的位置，傍晚時分坐在這裡可以一邊享受美食，一邊欣賞絕美的夕陽景色。夕陽的餘暉灑在桌上，增添了一份浪漫和溫馨（Romeo Engkong提供）<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GzoxcUjds-rwEr5IkjCsxYhYwlmlhrRZkToJjvAbtSwGfFj6vbyqmzJkMDym7FSWX_m7mH4Q02kdIj3QOKQx4rnylBTD9mZJ5dhJM7qEDCGPtcbb1O-7w4bzZUWBjesCDz-nBZM3RH5ZGgk6EEB8mxiAi_C3gVlfWufhixjp4EZyoseXHeDaLNoVNE4MVU4S-yO3uKO2fCTLXL5CznUq7fyLmkf9DDa8OYirWLsz7egt0cp31zFQ8XNzTU?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwiiIzPnbNr8Y5RA45s0KQMxuiXlxMeAEmE_2wpTIqdGxQ54S94DHSB3L0KYbwbGqPXRY4gny5VijdhtaV9mySb9dFlwmLfPxDDTDiR0QTrZqhrD15EPCMeqynX0iTB2WGbFk5q6WeNr0ufj5fmDXIAWb64FL3kI_vMt5wpdAXGuACJhNpBfzBVvU_6U4jCxf0WXwrty2yNmqEpZCMRL9VEJYY4A_8deKpwI8TlQR9sBPaomilgUh9QTE0?authuser=0&fife=s16383 https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GzoxcUjds-rwEr5IkjCsxYhYwlmlhrRZkToJjvAbtSwGfFj6vbyqmzJkMDym7FSWX_m7mH4Q02kdIj3QOKQx4rnylBTD9mZJ5dhJM7qEDCGPtcbb1O-7w4bzZUWBjesCDz-nBZM3RH5ZGgk6EEB8mxiAi_C3gVlfWufhixjp4EZyoseXHeDaLNoVNE4MVU4S-yO3uKO2fCTLXL5CznUq7fyLmkf9DDa8OYirWLsz7egt0cp31zFQ8XNzTU?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2660894,-8.5165163,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>La Baracca Bali (Ubud)</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gzhi0t-b4HLm86bezbj4UAATLlnXH01IXFoiFDFrV8Qx1Q6RTW7n3r0TbBJznfuLINbMO2xQ3KNoODwPB7xB3Z2oBxwdtdadRxV4B9DNyoxY44qYTWtKowOazqblL8gGH0bUwVa2_gbnEt3gj9DIMYRQ-oH16UoldtdoCwHc2cvY17E1t-_rwe4I0WqUXnUZGQ5Nd3HFgNAUdFtC-uMhUIJTRlKZU3I3RpOa0iuQSfjypCqW88l_CP6zDU?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>靠近烏布皇宮，很好吃的Pizza，也有義大利麵跟小點<br>Google map 平均4.6的高分，調酒也不錯，餐廳氛圍很好<br>一個人吃一個pizza有點太多，我打包回家繼續吃，冷掉也很好吃<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gzhi0t-b4HLm86bezbj4UAATLlnXH01IXFoiFDFrV8Qx1Q6RTW7n3r0TbBJznfuLINbMO2xQ3KNoODwPB7xB3Z2oBxwdtdadRxV4B9DNyoxY44qYTWtKowOazqblL8gGH0bUwVa2_gbnEt3gj9DIMYRQ-oH16UoldtdoCwHc2cvY17E1t-_rwe4I0WqUXnUZGQ5Nd3HFgNAUdFtC-uMhUIJTRlKZU3I3RpOa0iuQSfjypCqW88l_CP6zDU?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2636298,-8.503982,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Warung Pulau Kelapa Organic Garden</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwbEGNlyGKwvwcgDeXdfTCsDPCbIOJlFSqHGgpsqSzk3Xoos9Lh6SjJH07n4i4RPcBdydAn0_eNGWJbEF9xLDN3NnyKJiSV1BMT3uD-b13N04eZcZx8q-JolwLIz_xNpHh7E1duFUG94LnEZjK8tbyfnZwlysAUDHSJhW3wYAH5daLKwkWWW9K5xlNbB4zuAyVAVs_xTxT_PM2jLxnIAt312eGbKEazAtjo_Sp_B0lAKRSW22wx3bsDRaQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>印尼料理，餐廳大座位舒適，菜單種類很多<br>（旁邊是Putri Bali Spa 一店，可以按完摩來吃）<br><br>我第一次來吃是一個人，只點了一碗麵，感受不大<br>後來跟朋友再訪，大家人數多，餐點點了很多<br>這家餐點選項很多，我們點了一大輪，炒飯炒麵青菜都點，都不錯<br>印象深刻是：豬叻牌很好吃，沙爹也很好吃<br>這家餐廳位子很多，裝潢跟服務都中上，而且菜都是自己種的，我覺得很不錯！<br><br>想吃好吃印尼餐廳，可以安排這家！<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwbEGNlyGKwvwcgDeXdfTCsDPCbIOJlFSqHGgpsqSzk3Xoos9Lh6SjJH07n4i4RPcBdydAn0_eNGWJbEF9xLDN3NnyKJiSV1BMT3uD-b13N04eZcZx8q-JolwLIz_xNpHh7E1duFUG94LnEZjK8tbyfnZwlysAUDHSJhW3wYAH5daLKwkWWW9K5xlNbB4zuAyVAVs_xTxT_PM2jLxnIAt312eGbKEazAtjo_Sp_B0lAKRSW22wx3bsDRaQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2524802,-8.4950207,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Pison, Ubud</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GylpEl-aQ1Vx6w5IizkMqazRBFLrONPA-0AyLA6hi_An38ccmiUtARWs3uxV79_XQfCDOLzqMicJ4ipeISlHzk9KQjaa1BbWQrMx0_kiyQy7Yil3XX5WCpJGz33seEhq7A7nNsWvQK4DC5UoT70Lq7zKlFXv5SW95WL1Pg2tcGKJ-dN8a7fqWb43V_ksadsSlirdTsMzIjh6z9s_lc4xuJj2yohtSwTxc_2pJWFnRJF8vioXC5bo4fmFAE?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>咖啡廳，莎拉、漢堡、三明治、咖啡、調酒等，種類很多<br>有室內跟室外空間，室外是坐在田旁邊，很舒服<br>我最愛最愛吃的組合是：冰拿鐵（很濃，冰塊是牛奶）＋雞肉沙拉（沙拉醬是青醬，味道好好！），這個組合我吃了三次！因為太喜歡了～很合我的胃！<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GylpEl-aQ1Vx6w5IizkMqazRBFLrONPA-0AyLA6hi_An38ccmiUtARWs3uxV79_XQfCDOLzqMicJ4ipeISlHzk9KQjaa1BbWQrMx0_kiyQy7Yil3XX5WCpJGz33seEhq7A7nNsWvQK4DC5UoT70Lq7zKlFXv5SW95WL1Pg2tcGKJ-dN8a7fqWb43V_ksadsSlirdTsMzIjh6z9s_lc4xuJj2yohtSwTxc_2pJWFnRJF8vioXC5bo4fmFAE?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2636307,-8.5182718,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Muse Cafe & Art]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GyPHYco0FCREt22ZjLuXhiGvF0FP_7qDSEHP7tRb3Ja7yLSI-3Tszo1wcEJS8IQDc08biDVc-L6LHSmhOhsb1QVoaVTdoouoVvJSuFu8PBP1KZqyFCFBOmNbLiOMmrXQKFMioHDBvI7WZHfHLjkM3cq0TXA3j_LVc3CIiolbQzMmP-FJj_x1T5BEMjfKdEAA9dQl4NCZYt3O5dMtukauD4A0TL2WLq4sgJzi81wgwH2xhdux6MM9pmo4C0?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>座位空間很棒，是半開放式的空間，待在這邊很舒服，連洗手間都設計得很漂亮<br>我吃酪梨三明治味道一般，咖啡好喝，看評論寫印度菜很好吃，也許可以試試！<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GyPHYco0FCREt22ZjLuXhiGvF0FP_7qDSEHP7tRb3Ja7yLSI-3Tszo1wcEJS8IQDc08biDVc-L6LHSmhOhsb1QVoaVTdoouoVvJSuFu8PBP1KZqyFCFBOmNbLiOMmrXQKFMioHDBvI7WZHfHLjkM3cq0TXA3j_LVc3CIiolbQzMmP-FJj_x1T5BEMjfKdEAA9dQl4NCZYt3O5dMtukauD4A0TL2WLq4sgJzi81wgwH2xhdux6MM9pmo4C0?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
