        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2664463,-8.4941544,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Warung Makan Bu Rus</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gy6i8ZM6cDWbBigofEVNXvGDiPc9kDc6vXruEqXOI6ommZYarFosKj5w0k87RJplVCxA_wUxqUcV17ZUBpxBK5eSVIDCaPyN2ip26kxuOP-a4JoSyXPdKTz5rYqDlR-GD2T-4cO3eLqy4-DwtU8uXZ7CQ28hf4Dl5iC2ii-DdGbVCtfoZuMu4VAuSei19vFgbBF-B2v77Rtjj5fxijmzRZcRGzxJy8prI9zhu4iOprChfBkPAX5PTFYMTY?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>印尼料理，被門口的燒烤沙爹香味吸引進去<br>一盤沙爹飯＋一杯調酒，結帳時台幣一百多塊，嚇一跳便宜<br>用餐時間排隊的人很多，便宜好吃的店！<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gy6i8ZM6cDWbBigofEVNXvGDiPc9kDc6vXruEqXOI6ommZYarFosKj5w0k87RJplVCxA_wUxqUcV17ZUBpxBK5eSVIDCaPyN2ip26kxuOP-a4JoSyXPdKTz5rYqDlR-GD2T-4cO3eLqy4-DwtU8uXZ7CQ28hf4Dl5iC2ii-DdGbVCtfoZuMu4VAuSei19vFgbBF-B2v77Rtjj5fxijmzRZcRGzxJy8prI9zhu4iOprChfBkPAX5PTFYMTY?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
