      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Tree of Chocolate by Adriana</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gw8Q8XFqp6KlVnGGOWAWgpu2LVRmSJumJA9fDNgK-8vHggKeoQAYJqgLreuXlCGsS0ayAjbyjo6xe7yfGWONe94AXtOnMJUwtuh0ocx-WJKosF0sV7Mw0bf4ufltKNyg_EquCJV2C33mKf_ii2wU3mhQd04yIGHEbn-a2FOEtwbUA7BtVJ35FB0DR88UTGniSIxdgiHxXSpIj9_tbh-ZUhG5e7hz_ZPDTUMuVMbO9RLp1m_CQS3z4xvsj0?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Radiantly Alive瑜伽教室旁邊挖掘到的巧克力專門店，散步經過心血來潮想說買一塊吃吃看，然後好吃到又買了三塊不同口味在店裡吃<br>店內是半開放式的廚房，員工們正在製作巧克力，招呼十分親切熱情<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
