      <Placemark>
        <name>Donna</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gw9h-oT97_QHt33pW61qCVau_WO8raueqjj9F1U_0qwA_kBWFfOxEYMjezpv-SGdOZfYaLgaRihGF4o0ylHFXsJ6Cz1guhnwJVrLDSJtXKHob_siF-Dwhy_OqacKjSH9jMEAITpNyryZQInnF8LeMvM5sLuN1ZUlX_nZ9-H-_7zUtTTJ19hA0Um6sZ_auNfI6Sidg6IJviP9FSUmQyDDgXRDyQAw0yzRKlP7xkHVDAjW-oiNA5SIxW0qGI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>義大利麵很好吃！我點的這杯調酒還好，餐廳裝潢滿時髦的，就在烏布熱鬧的街附近（有許多報導說這家調酒很推薦，可以試試看）<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
