      <Placemark>
        <name>Sinssihwaro Korean BBQ</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gw2CCPw0gDlpS3ZoCF_jcgD6ZosTYDAL5myP3CuA_WokucOeNSSJXLvEvUmP--Xww0CBKHhXVgLUjQmnh-D_k_uQc8t6vaETgmREMA7hMriHGPJGadsFBSJgzNbNIwbcvfoDwnEkBFLdBKYM2PFGG7GoIBVUafHVqeOXn3-n_xNXsM8xoe96pOPzCZn93edGoV8GmWHCiXJqWc8X3MLv4GUFvxzoi-Uk_6JP3uyxtP1Zb87lgx6h_cn090?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>走經過都被店的裝潢給吸引，門是全開放的，韓國料理店<br>燒肉可以選擇公克數，也可以選自己烤還是店家烤（我選店家烤XD） 好吃～<br>一個人吃韓式涼麵份量太多，又太辣，吃兩口就吃不下了<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gw2CCPw0gDlpS3ZoCF_jcgD6ZosTYDAL5myP3CuA_WokucOeNSSJXLvEvUmP--Xww0CBKHhXVgLUjQmnh-D_k_uQc8t6vaETgmREMA7hMriHGPJGadsFBSJgzNbNIwbcvfoDwnEkBFLdBKYM2PFGG7GoIBVUafHVqeOXn3-n_xNXsM8xoe96pOPzCZn93edGoV8GmWHCiXJqWc8X3MLv4GUFvxzoi-Uk_6JP3uyxtP1Zb87lgx6h_cn090?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
