      <Placemark>
        <name>Lazy Cats Cafe</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GzDaEX0Ukzl6D0A5C0zrKWQwaC0Ve2Ife5mr94vfC56Gr4bINJxOULRb5vtdBErH9_hiTOc1CHxnnEDLGSgr_oApdKiW0jMkH2mhq8IQxrrGEA0FNIrxABfZVXeD8qYYlHCJmkDFNJm_kPl_-PZN717r14eVxxQWP5Y6VAIfgmnHfobSS1JondtK3udL_9Hm1fOqd7kxiy4uKO5BGh3Zn9abeGgu7kgIoysvxqQZg8oRzyRwWjKiqJ7Vuk?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>素食咖啡廳，店內很漂亮！從一樓上來開始，牆壁上掛各種畫 氛圍不錯<br>這邊的酪梨三明治就很好吃！<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
