      <Placemark>
        <name>Monsieur Spoon Ubud</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gx12fmWIiCRN0WQesq0udkOEVrZF_T5Mo2ekU2tSMV-F9idUTiblM41anhRV8EAnnMFOlbbhGy5lVB3saqnhl9mCseE3w6xzmXzWZo4bslybq-pi5FSCF1nF04hOnOsR7LTvIlTz1XFB8waZQTmtTHPi_zcO2Voy8c3iY_DOA9FPpO1OFTGAJxMoqcRApR54EfD2T-XJ64rvj-RuWujU83et3qScuy-G1kFQ2vM4gqm5ipIcOhNNsYZ4JE?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>可頌很有名！在Yoga Barn跟Pison附近，我吃過一次，印象不錯<br>來喝個咖啡配可頌很讚<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
