      <Placemark>
        <name>The Lair</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GzSPhruVVLogy1SW-1R60jd0B_-OKQ3z4ab1lGnqwpd-p3Iz75fT12xWMqWKxrAl0FAW17mJubkpnZXDgh4tIiVkd2Dxq5jK746gS64sokn-VC8GeOjgFxemXBCQZNswW5vNK7yMappD_sNgqd0pcNWbOlRLt-6unPoAQ9BJvFsIHb0JJiWlJOjdRHSnb3wbLiU_CtpUrzyDQpILurwBG282ViPlVllfADS2z3jzlXOSVWV8VK5skI4_ck?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>酒吧，要先走下一個樓梯（有點地窖感），掀開布帘，神秘隱密的空間<br>然後是半開放式的空間，靠窗的位子是直接面對一片森林<br>酒單是像撲克牌一樣，一張一張的，很可愛！<br>調酒好喝、裝潢很讚、氣氛很好、現場有DJ放歌<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
