      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>KAWI UBUD</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gz4Wdfd-SG_ibhlDwIGAIzO7ubi-wD525kyzlCSv8SEThbICvpi7eQFL-SQbpquwRRQlS3208-pUpuvB36UyrF27UFzoU6pr5gYvqaHKO7hsNb_qGaY2Rw1QhegQTEDHsy8AOe5_nJJrKIQKeltzYSSQpEkQ7OwqwSn3Extfm9YvhegmL7qB2i773J99PZzcd4ZgjcT3hZtCkvDpLmSFYgmlAEGn34aRUUmRcNQhD4J4CLNzNKmESQlWnQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>酒吧，店的位子有一點偏遠，門口很暗，要找一下<br>內部裝潢是日系簡約感，內部很暗，，座位很少，調酒總類不多<br>但！黃色杯子這杯是我心目中第一名好喝！！（以我這趟峇里島所有喝到的調酒來說）下面熱巧克力酒＋上面冰奶泡，很綿密，鹹鹹甜甜的，喝下去很驚艷！<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
