      <Placemark>
        <name>Night Rooster</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwmSduQO2q0tL41Mzb7Pep2IqUTKg_7iZCmDm3nlo6maubaGu2sVtRtvPUthlKlA1IXlDUOhGkRiRjcNXxNFrzHiWOrETmaTW86_lBWklKkAEwP6A9l_lZvggEcnOAtEK5nZZRrKfRxyKd1dO8wrcUQd8ZG0QGCbxFHNFhI_c1n6CQglK3o-g7XNY6yv70sHskRTI782csT9eHZwqUxINYyj_rtjmcfVow7uIyc7z1UoAjnnxp4IjuqZlI?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>酒吧，被裡面的裝潢經驗到，很漂亮時髦，酒單設計得超可愛<br>一坐下來就會有一大碗炸薯片，調酒都是跟峇里島元素結合<br>這家是所有酒吧中單價最高的，我喝了兩杯調酒，結帳時台幣快八百元<br>裝潢精緻、調酒總類豐富、氣氛很棒<br><br>三家酒吧中，這家是最接近烏布皇宮的，走路到，很近<br><br>Nikki提供：https://vocus.cc/article/64785ee1fd8978000187e1e6]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GwmSduQO2q0tL41Mzb7Pep2IqUTKg_7iZCmDm3nlo6maubaGu2sVtRtvPUthlKlA1IXlDUOhGkRiRjcNXxNFrzHiWOrETmaTW86_lBWklKkAEwP6A9l_lZvggEcnOAtEK5nZZRrKfRxyKd1dO8wrcUQd8ZG0QGCbxFHNFhI_c1n6CQglK3o-g7XNY6yv70sHskRTI782csT9eHZwqUxINYyj_rtjmcfVow7uIyc7z1UoAjnnxp4IjuqZlI?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
