      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Sun Sun Warung</name>
        <description><![CDATA[價格實惠又好吃的印尼菜餐廳<br><br>隱身在烏布的小巷弄內<br>我們午餐這天幸好沒排隊, 進入後就有位子坐了<br>點了酥炸鴨, 烤鴨, 混和飯NASI CAMPUR <br>沙嗲, 春捲, 及甜點椰絲捲<br>家人們覺得混和飯比較不合胃口<br>烤鴨跟炸鴨都好吃, 超酥脆的春捲及甜點椰絲捲必點<br>他們也有賣吃沙嗲沾的花生醬跟辣椒叄巴醬（李秋雄提供）]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.2669234,-8.5091172,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Bird's Nest Thai Kitchen]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GxLr12gT_DshWrslYsrV0wUqy5zJq-Tb5Pk0E9OiirOeV3ZwV8HfefOMHJWtiZ_IaA9pPXViDHtERFC2WZRv9D4LtxIDo4fnwrqjcmONCChZRgcxTGofdXNM8YEwUKJ-kx1ew-iaCnyZCGpB6GP8_JxwkOdXM1xiR3XrG3LSeMPaya46AelG_0xPFAZNy48tFpowAoPzic2-kxsJzJfklzKuxuLG_Fyms_a_p654Q5crPwK02kkq3idx1E?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Chien Chi Huang提供:<br>泰式料理 Bird’s Nest Thai Kitchen好吃，Canggu也有一家。<br>照片這樣約台幣600，炒飯份量超大，冬蔭功跟在泰國吃到的一模一樣！超好吃！<br>脆皮豬有點太硬了，個人不愛，炒飯不會太乾卻又粒粒分明，有鍋氣且很香，不膩！超推]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
