      <Placemark>
        <name>Grand Puncak Sari Restaurant</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gy1nqriwrOp31-4yQcKsjIcs_OlPhZxJfRm-yHR3pYuhXrvwrZEbI3Dq7-hSFTde5Ia48ouzQSBjlvY0PHuz1mB_Kl9oUAdwIbaz15mR-3_FKo7DLN9pl8edfqezfAJ1U2Q9IKtnHO23vxTw7MCYftiWAoFegNib4NCK_MMpe0GnjPMJTtkZHFcorUxTHsnBD-7ULIrRM12q-IaYsKQV-MAP_DPI8G-lw_MtpBvGjJ6oL1lo1bL6IfGYRo?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>位於金塔瑪尼的火山景觀餐廳<br>原本只想找這個地方看看火山<br>對食物並不抱任何期待, 結果竟出乎意料的還不錯<br>有Buffet自助式吃到飽與單點的用餐方式, 我們是選擇Buffet <br>吃到飽一個人的用餐費用是300台幣<br>食物就是一些在地的料理, 炒麵.炒飯.沙嗲和一些炸物及湯品<br>都不錯吃真的令我訝異, 以300塊的價值我覺得很不錯了（李秋雄、何志慶提供）<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_Gzimu7sNqVXEHYqB73ARJsaHSKB5eROsHc5yiytIg9DPoiQtViAYy27YPuZCxe6jyl6X-uZufBykC3sREG3Og-IXOCgibtLXCLDnbouU9roIFzNc0jnXzjy6-cJA1yM1B9muSQkldLMhTrk-vnIJ225P0HKI6vHGCHftykfjBZ_kgt_u6WKS1Fpay24ZsG1iC1uTUDyydt5j_Pa1f9OyvvwUSwgrOxKxs3OIeMsd4B0r4TQLoZsj5ghnj0?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AE5a_GyPgdAa_xgUrwiW4EbQFKP8wzpmCPmOS4RoKhMqkqkD-3tOeKzZqAihu5xbfpKxK6TkEyYjMNfO-xy0d7r1FXDVSH68Oz_XchpRW3f_QLy8KMOkYLdDdFTZSvgstwrMtOaHy1WmzOB7YSXUpK6IPTwSMUoUTLqolVpSSBvIIIgMZsEeMZFN4t5X1yT32cet8axTzhpPpYcsWax8_PIuLg5ZR4N_fUYWrX9Y2jP-zW89DBX7aZRPglaFIcM?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1899-0288D1</styleUrl>
